      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n        \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/png;base64,\u003d\" \r\n        alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eEquipment Predictive Maintenance\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThis app helps businesses prevent equipment failure by predicting when maintenance is needed before breakdowns happen. It combines machine learning, root cause analysis, and real-time equipment data to reduce downtime, cut costs, and improve asset reliability.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eUsers upload equipment and sensor data, including criticality, condition states, asset types, and historical maintenance records.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThe app predicts upcoming maintenance needs, highlights high-risk assets, and provides RCA insights and visual trends to support proactive maintenance planning.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eSmart Maintenance Prediction: Uses H2O ML models to forecast equipment servicing needs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eRoot Cause Analysis (RCA): Detects recurring failure patterns and explains potential causes.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eAdvanced Visualization: Tracks metrics across asset categories, condition states, and criticality